item.title: Netaus
item.dc:creator: Shaggy
item.description:
\\|ShotintheDark|/:

Been lurking around these forums for quite a while, and out of all the shit I’ve seen posted here now and then, I must regress…

So far, it’s looking like quite the kickass map, good sir.

Just curious, but is there any backstory to this map? I see in your first screenshot that there seems to be a metallic, un-earthly surface in the upper-right hand corner of the shot. Human, or otherwise?

Well to be honest that’s one part where i do tests with source engine and then i put them in the map.
Anyway yes, there’s a backstory but I’m working on it.
I deleted the screenshot because I do not like it

Edit: i have some new screens:

  • Freezer aisle.

  • A fan in the freezer sector.


-Corridor that leads into the canals.

  • Nothing of interesting.
